rmal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我相信天網恢恢 疏而不漏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 七警是例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 各位小學中學雞好好做個聽話既良民啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"983a0b13b0cbba9a87c392decfa8f2f30bbe73b0","tid":139300,"uid":40763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T02:37:42.000Z","msg":"樓主就係個男朋友<br />\n完"},{"pid":"ce23cb1df71ff2f325c7a9538ef6ec09a192a94c","tid":139300,"uid":23364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T02:42:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講真啦 做果時就你情我願 分左手就反轉豬肚 又話告人又盛 香港呢個社會就係太照顧女人 先會有d 咁既人出現 鬼唔望樓主仆街死</blockquote><br />\n啲女真係戇鳩鳩唔用腦諗野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n因為想同人一齊返 就屈鳩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n天大笑話"},{"pid":"d770fb769ba596780cc8b530c53a08bd5dcf3e93","tid":139300,"uid":83063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T02:42:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>真係仆街嚟<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n講緊你同條臭雞</blockquote><br />\n係呀我都覺得佢好仆街，不過又想告唔告得入喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睇人仆街最開心</blockquote><br />\n其實告唔入    如果法官知道佢地岩岩分手  女仔想復合  男又唔肯   有屈人既動機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fc7b8fb9567ce4e184c7aeb0fa5152bd9a7dace","tid":139300,"uid":11895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-02T02:50:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>兩年前你點證明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔怪得咁快比人呃左隻豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都無腦既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/1